CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773857158
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners have
OL,4,Cwitnessed 'violence and abuse while
OL,5,Cshopping'
OL,7,FThe picture was a little different for
OL,8,Fthose witnessing shop theft, topped by
OL,9,FLondon and the West Midlands at 29%.
OL,11,FRetailers reported that organised
OL,12,Fcriminal gangs were increasingly
OL,13,Ftargeting high-value goods that they
OL,14,Fcan easily resell.
OL,16,FPrevious BRC data revealed there were
OL,17,F1,600 incidents of violence and abuse
OL,18,Fagainst retail workers every day last
OL,19,Fyear nationally, the second highest
OL,20,Flevel on record.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
