FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773857158
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners have
OL,4,Cwitnessed 'violence and abuse while
OL,5,Cshopping'
OL,7,FThe BRC said delivery drivers were
OL,8,Falso often subjected to abuse,
OL,9,Fphysical violence and threats with
OL,10,Fweapons.
OL,12,FIt said retailers had spent an
OL,13,Festimated #5 billion on fighting
OL,14,Fretail crime over the past five years,
OL,15,Fincluding on CCTV, security personnel,
OL,16,Fanti-theft devices and body-worn
OL,17,Fcameras.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
