OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773857158
OL,3,CAlmost a third of Londoners have
OL,4,Cwitnessed 'violence and abuse while
OL,5,Cshopping'
OL,7,FThese costs added to existing
OL,8,Ffinancial pressures, limited
OL,9,Finvestment and contributed to higher
OL,10,Fprices for customers, it warned.
OL,12,FThe upcoming Crime and Policing Bill
OL,13,Fwill remove the #200 threshold of "low
OL,14,Flevel" theft, "sending a clear signal
OL,15,Fthat all shoplifting will be treated
OL,16,Fseriously", the BRC said.
OL,18,FHowever, it said the Bill needed to go
OL,19,Ffurther by extending protection to all
OL,20,Fcustomer-facing retail workers,
OL,21,Fincluding delivery drivers.
OL,26,@uD@cOUvD@FO]vD@OOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
